subject: HISTORY
text: Give the century, B.C. or A.D., of each of the following, indicate who or what each was, and say why each is important in history: Treaty of Wedmore, John Hampden, Sir John Hawkins, Award of Norham, Battle of Bosworth, Edward Gibbon Wakefield, Sir Isaac Newton, St. Benedict, the Fronde, Charles Martel.
